---
source: crates/runtime/tests/search/mod.rs
description: "SELECT id, answer, trunc(_score, 3) as _score FROM vector_search(qs, 'secondary', answer) where subject!='math' order by _score desc, id LIMIT 4"
---
+---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                               |
+---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: _score DESC NULLS FIRST, vector_search(qs, Utf8("secondary"), answer).id ASC NULLS LAST, fetch=4                                                                                             |
|               |   Projection: vector_search(qs, Utf8("secondary"), answer).id, vector_search(qs, Utf8("secondary"), answer).answer, trunc(vector_search(qs, Utf8("secondary"), answer)._score, Int64(3)) AS _score |
|               |     TableScan: vector_search(qs, Utf8("secondary"), answer) projection=[_score, answer, id], full_filters=[vector_search(qs, Utf8("secondary"), answer).subject != Utf8("math")]                   |
| physical_plan | SortPreservingMergeExec: [_score@2 DESC, id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], fetch=4                                                                                                                             |
|               |   SortExec: TopK(fetch=4), expr=[_score@2 DESC, id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                 |
|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[id@2 as id, answer@1 as answer, trunc(_score@0, 3) as _score]                                                                                                            |
|               |       RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                         |
|               |         ProjectionExec: expr=[_score@1 as _score, answer@2 as answer, id@0 as id]                                                                                                                  |
|               |           HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=Left, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(id@0, id@1)], filter=subject@0 != math, projection=[id@0, _score@2, answer@3]                    |
|               |             CoalescePartitionsExec                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |               ProjectionExec: expr=[CAST(key@1 AS Int64) as id, subject@0 as subject, 1 - distance@2 as _score]                                                                                    |
|               |                 CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |                   RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                             |
|               |                     BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |                       CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |                         S3VectorsQueryExec (INDEX_NAME_1): filter={subject:{$ne:"math"}} limit=100                                                                                                 |
|               |             SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |               BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |                 DataSourceExec: partitions=1, partition_sizes=[1]                                                                                                                                  |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
+---------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
